Create an image titled 'Vanilla Sugar in the Style of Salvador Dali.' Imagine the crystals of vanilla sugar transforming into surreal forms characteristic of Dali's style. In the background, include a melted pocket watch gently flowing over the edge of a sugar mound, while the sugar crystals themselves morph into bizarre shapes and figures reminiscent of Dali's paintings. Add soft, curved lines and unexpected details to create an atmosphere of dreams and fantasies.
